<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM4.10.2">
<l>nāṭi nīrva ṇaṅkun teyvamu mummaiyu muṉpaṭaittāṉ</l>
<l>vīṭil cīrppuka ḻātippi rāṉavaṉ mēvi yuṟaikōyiṉ</l>
<l>māṭa māḷikai cūḻntaḻa kāya tirukkuru kūrataṉaip</l>
<l>pāṭi yāṭip paravic ceṉmiṉkaḷ pallula kīrparantē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The temple where he stays affectionately, the primeval lord praised for [his] excellence without dissolution,</l>
<l>he who once created you and the gods you seek out [and] bow to,</l>
<l>Tirukkurukūr that is beautiful, being surrounded by storied mansions [and] palaces,</l>
<l>go singing, dancing [and] reverring widely, o you of many worlds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
